#- Laws of Mine-Köping;§0
§0Do not take any dirt from the main isle.§0
§0Do not destroy other property.§0
§0Do not kill animals on the main isle.§0
§0Do not kill an other player unless the king has aproved it.§0
§0Do not take whats not yours.§0
